name: Among Us LORA v1
description:
The result of my experiment with trying to generate Among Us characters using AI, but this time using LORA compatible with various models.

To use the model, use:

Type "amongus" in a few places where you think it will work. Also, set the weight of the model to something like 0.7-0.8 like this: <lora:amongus:0.8>

Take a look at the example pictures where I tried to show connections with different base models and LORA

You can edit, improve and publish your version of the model as much as you want, but it would be nice if you could link me in the description when you're done :)
